{"tid":1636631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（純討論）亂用三罷呢個term有咩用","createTime":"2019-10-07T19:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T19:53:59.000Z","uid":318162,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee71d484875bcc5972bd7252e2a4d09a808b4f0","tid":1636631,"uid":318162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:06:06.000Z","msg":"見過好多次話三罷<br />\n但其實最真實嗰次係85三罷<br />\n其他都係得個名<br />\n<br />\n罷工罷市罷課<br />\n前兩者應該無乜<br />\n後者有少少人有做<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家唔好罷<br />\n只係覺得<br />\n但係你9用呢個term人哋只會習慣左呢個term而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n三罷得個term無影響力 無人做野只會degrade左個term<br />\n<br />\n有無另一啲字詞可代替？<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999唔知大家明唔明我想表達d咩<br />\n<br />\n錯左請大家提醒下🙏🏽"},{"pid":"e4be353e5aa88ac2a3ce96c680e976f9a043cabe","tid":1636631,"uid":186874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:08:14.000Z","msg":"（幫推上熱門）可唔可以推返啲正經野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1636594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1636594</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f34e2528599ec7377258334070d54a4bb8e99660","tid":1636631,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:14:31.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n最有效係85嗰次"},{"pid":"2763e8d7f8fc974e3800cd0a7edda73aed317f2b","tid":1636631,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:19:44.000Z","msg":"好大陸feel"},{"pid":"8416aaaed3d01a876d34d39457cd9ff5a7f3ec99","tid":1636631,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:45:27.000Z","msg":"算啦 香港唔會三罷 太多中資野"},{"pid":"f09731589f5edb490f904932057e3bbbc8940f72","tid":1636631,"uid":318162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8416aaaed3d01a876d34d39457cd9ff5a7f3ec99","tid":1636631,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:45:27.000Z","msg":"算啦 香港唔會三罷 太多中資野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:53:59.000Z","msg":"係唔想大家對三罷麻木<br />\n平日罷乜都好<br />\n<br />\n如果一提三罷<br />\n大家一齊做野<br />\n個效果其實會好好多？<br />\n<br />\n宜家呢個時勢都唔